    {
        "text": "So, now I'm here hoping to change the world to a place...",
        "startTime": 8590,
        "endTime": 11709,
        "slowStartTime": 13035,
        "slowEndTime": 17789
    },
    {
        "text": "...where all minorities can feel embraced.",
        "startTime": 12141,
        "endTime": 14418,
        "slowStartTime": 18361,
        "slowEndTime": 21852
    },
    {
        "text": "There was a horrific incident last year in Jerusalem...",
        "startTime": 16151,
        "endTime": 19470,
        "slowStartTime": 24377,
        "slowEndTime": 29430
    },
    {
        "text": "...when six people were stabbed in a hate crime attack...",
        "startTime": 19688,
        "endTime": 22659,
        "slowStartTime": 29682,
        "slowEndTime": 34213
    },
    {
        "text": "...at a gay pride parade.",
        "startTime": 23051,
        "endTime": 24444,
        "slowStartTime": 34726,
        "slowEndTime": 36891
    },
    {
        "text": "We hear shocking news of LGBT people being attacked and killed...",
        "startTime": 24990,
        "endTime": 28561,
        "slowStartTime": 37635,
        "slowEndTime": 43066
    },
    {
        "text": "...in hate crimes all around the world.",
        "startTime": 28651,
        "endTime": 30546,
        "slowStartTime": 43127,
        "slowEndTime": 46044
    },
    {
        "text": "However, for those of us living in Japan,...",
        "startTime": 31810,
        "endTime": 34453,
        "slowStartTime": 47865,
        "slowEndTime": 51905
    },
    {
        "text": "...this extreme violence is hard to understand,...",
        "startTime": 35028,
        "endTime": 38663,
        "slowStartTime": 52692,
        "slowEndTime": 58219
    },
    {
        "text": "...almost to the point of being unimaginable.",
        "startTime": 39153,
        "endTime": 41889,
        "slowStartTime": 58880,
        "slowEndTime": 63059
    },
    {
        "text": "So, does this make Japan a country that truly embraces diversity?",
        "startTime": 42623,
        "endTime": 46969,
        "slowStartTime": 64084,
        "slowEndTime": 70679
    },
    {
        "text": "My answer, sadly, is no.",
        "startTime": 48269,
        "endTime": 51067,
        "slowStartTime": 72553,
        "slowEndTime": 76826
    },
    {
        "text": "Japan, I feel, is still a closed and intolerant country.",
        "startTime": 52601,
        "endTime": 56173,
        "slowStartTime": 79051,
        "slowEndTime": 84485
    },
    {
        "text": "Let me give you an example.",
        "startTime": 56957,
        "endTime": 58238,
        "slowStartTime": 85585,
        "slowEndTime": 87582
    },
    {
        "text": "A boy at one of the top universities in Japan committed suicide...",
        "startTime": 58806,
        "endTime": 61937,
        "slowStartTime": 88359,
        "slowEndTime": 93130
    },
    {
        "text": "...after experiencing severe bullying for being gay.",
        "startTime": 62021,
        "endTime": 64819,
        "slowStartTime": 93181,
        "slowEndTime": 97454
    },
    {
